name: The New Nurses
overview: The lives of Erik and Anna, students at a nursing school in 1950s Denmark, a time and place where it was not normal for a man to become a nurse.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview:
Premier Danmark, 1/11-2021 På TV2 Charlie  Premier Sverige. 20/2-2023 på CMore klockan 00:01

New season: 'Sygeplejeskolen' gets a season 5  Nursing school season 4 Photo: Mike Kollöffel / TV 2  By TRINE JERICHAU ROSLEV  1 November 2021  The popular TV 2 series will have a new season in the coming year.  The fourth season of Sygeplejeskolen only just reached its end before TV 2 announced that the series will get another season:  New season about Anna and Ole  Mette Heiberg does not want to reveal much about the upcoming season, but if you follow Anna and Ole's relationship, there seems to be good news:  "(...)we must see, among other things, whether Anna and Ole's relationship can handle the challenges, now that Ole has been employed in Anna's father's company, and whether Nina and Bent will become a real 50s nuclear family with father, mother and child,"  says Heiberg about the fifth season.

episodes.name: Nye Tider
episodes.overview: A Danish hospital in the 1950s embarks on a radical experiment: training men a nurses.

episodes.name: Sandhedens Time
episodes.overview: The male students face expulsion for carelessly cleaning equipment.

episodes.name: Polio
episodes.overview: Erik volunteers in the polio ward as Anna uncovers a patient's embarrassing secret.

episodes.name: Hemmeligheder
episodes.overview: Susanne and Anna are at odds over how to treat a burn patient.

episodes.name: Liv & Død
episodes.overview: Susanne realizes she might have to leave the program and Erik ends up treating his own father.

episodes.name: Exam
episodes.overview: Erik feels like a misfit as the probationary period comes to an end.

episodes.name: Det hvide snit/ The White Cut
Miraklet
episodes.overview: Fredenslund is being renovated, and Ms. Madsen is very unhappy about all the noise. A routine surgery goes mysteriously wrong - to Dr. Neumann and Anna's great dismay and surprise. While Nina tries to hide how far along she is in her pregnancy, Bent tries to come up with names for the baby. An old friend of the Matron is admitted, but he doesn't want the Matron to know.

episodes.name: Farlige stråler
episodes.overview: After a month in the radium department, Marie finally returns to wing B exhausted - along with Bjørn, no less. But her happiness is short-lived, as Ms. Madsen intervenes to send Marie back to the radium department, where her health begins to deteriorate. Bjørn goes to extreme measures to help her. Birgit is ready to return to work as a stewardess, but things don't go according to plan. And Ruth feels passed over, while the Matron starts to question whether she made the right decision.

episodes.name: Amerikanerpigen
episodes.overview: Else is put in charge of a young girl suffering from abdominal pain, and looks on in envy as the girl is showered with gifts from an American soldier. So when an opportunity presents itself, Else helps herself to the spoils. Dr. Friis' parents come for a visit, but leave both Dr. Friis and Lis feeling hurt. The Matron is in love with Klaus, but since he is still a patient, they can't spend any time together. Finally, Ole plans a surprise for Anna for her birthday

episodes.name: Blind Tro
episodes.overview: Anna has forgotten to inform her fellow students about the arrival of English nursing students at Fredenslund. Aksel becomes smitten with one of the English girls. Peter helps a visually impaired woman about to undergo surgery performed by the busy John. When Klaus is admitted again, Margrethe worries and urges the staff to find the cause of his symptoms. And in an effort to help Nina, John presents her with an even more difficult dilemma.

episodes.name: På Afveje
episodes.overview: An advertising executive entertains the entire ward with the story of his injuries while waiting to be discharged. Unfortunately, he cannot be discharged just yet, so Lis seizes the opportunity to try her hand at a new line of work. Anna is saved from yet another sticky situation, but finds it hard to be happy and grateful. Bent plans a surprise for Nina, which doesn't go exactly according to plan. Aksel learns the truth about Michelle, and a desperate Else tries to get Finn's attention.

episodes.name: Fatal Fejl
episodes.overview: A single mother and her daughter are admitted to Fredenslund under suspicion of ingesting poison. Anna puts everything on the line to help the mother out of her predicament. Nina and Bent are busy planning their wedding when John puts it all on the table for Nina. Margrethe finally stops trying to control things and lets her emotions run their course. And Bjørn and Marie get back together, but their happy reunion is cut short by the sound of an alarm.
